{"tid":2030742,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【美國亮劍】特朗普政府正探討恢復核試（FCed by 華盛頓郵報）","createTime":"2020-05-23T03:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T03:31:36.000Z","uid":48040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"511685974345b9e2e21096394063985763baaaa7","tid":2030742,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/trump-administration-discussed-conducting-first-us-nuclear-test-in-decades/2020/05/22/a805c904-9c5b-11ea-b60c-3be060a4f8e1_story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2Ftrump-administration-discussed-conducting-first-us-nuclear-test-in-decades%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2Fa805c904-9c5b-11ea-b60c-3be060a4f8e1_story.html&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=1bced50d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/trump-administration-discussed-conducting-first-us-nuclear-test-in-decades/2020/05/22/a805c904-9c5b-11ea-b60c-3be060a4f8e1_story.html</a><br />\n《華盛頓郵報》報導，5月15日美國國家安全機構的高級官員開會討論，美國是否應該重新恢復核試（美國上一次核試為1992年）。<br />\n有一名現任高級官員及兩名前官員向《華盛頓郵報》證實，近期有情報顯示，中國及俄羅斯都秘密進行了核武器試驗，為了震攝中俄這兩個核子武器大國，美國應該顯示自己也擁有迅速進行核試的能力。<br />\n消息人士指會議上並沒有達成最終結論，但強調未來會繼續討論。<br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n請支持黃channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_OtH-ee5lSw&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=b2aac20c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw</a>"}]}